data.description: All Brick Rambler on over an acre located within minutes of I-95 exit 104 but in a private setting.  Home features a large covered front porch which over sees the large cleared front yard with a beautiful mature Magnolia Tree.  Inside the home is plenty of wood flooring and 4 well sized Bedrooms. The Family room has a wood insert fireplace and the Living room offers plenty of sunlight.  The rear yard features a couple smaller storage storage sheds, however there is also a large run in style storage shed as well as an enormous Greenhouse.   This is one you will definitely want to grab your agent to see.  AGENTS:  Be Sure to Read Agent Remarks BEFORE Showing the property.  All showings must be scheduled in MLS.
